Package Algorithm

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    closestFruit
    this class implements an object of the shortest path algorithem, its contain the packman, the fruit and the time it took to get to this fruit.
    multiCsv
    this class has a function that need to run over a folder of files and find the csv one and translate it to a GIS project object.
    Path
    this class implement a path object.
    Path2KML
    this class convert all the paths of the game to a kml file, we can also see the fruits go away from the map when the packman gets and eats them.
    ShortestPathAlgo
    this class is a function to calculate a path of each packman to the fruits.
    sortComperator
    this class is a comperator to the arraylist of fruit we have so we can sort it from the closest to the farest.
